name: Summit Air ATR 72-202 [C-GUSA] Landing at Edmonton Airport ᴴᴰ
description:
Despite having over 600 videos on this channel, this is my first time ever filming an ATR! Here we have "Summit 7201" landing on runway 20 at Edmonton International Airport, arriving from Yellowknife on what I believe was a ferry flight (since no passengers actually got off). ATC is included, hope you enjoy this quick clip of my first ATR!

Thanks for watching!
